### Get all persons
GET http://localhost:8080/persons
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}


### Get person by id
GET http://localhost:8080/persons/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}


### Patch person by id
PATCH http://localhost:8080/persons/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "username": "Michael2"
}


### Delete person by id
DELETE http://localhost:8080/persons/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

